quran[8{c,v,t}:
41,39,"aur Allah ki nshanyon mein se aik yeh hai ke tum dekhte ho zameen sooni pari hui hai, phir jounhi ke hum ne is par pani barsaya, yakayak woh پھبک uthti hai aur phool jati hai yaqeenan jo khuda is meri hui zameen ko jala uthata hai woh mُrdon ko bhi zindagi bakhsnay wala hai yaqeenan woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
41,40,"jo log hamari ayaat ko ultay maienay p_hnate hain woh hum se kuch chupay hue nahi hain khud hi soch lau ke aaya woh shakhs behtar hai jo aag mein jhaunka jaane wala hai ya woh jo qayamat ke roz aman ki haalat mein haazir ho ga? karte raho jo kuch tum chaho, tumhari saari harkato ko Allah dekh raha hai"
41,41,yeh woh log hain jin ke samnay kalaam nasiyaat aaya to unhon ne usay maan-ne se inkaar kar diya magar haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh aik zabardast kitaab hai
41,42,"baatil nah samnay se is par aa sakta hai nah peechay se, yeh aik hakeem o hammeed ki nazil kardah cheez hai"
41,43,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se jo kuch kaha ja raha hai is mein koi cheez bhi aisi nahi hai jo tum se pehlay guzray hue Rasolo-n se nah kahi ja chuki ho be shak tumhara rab bara dar guzar karne wala hai, aur is ke sath barri dard naak saza dainay wala bhi hai"
41,44,"agar hum iss ko ajmi quran bana kar bhaijtay to yeh log kehte"" kyun nah is ki ayaat khol kar bayan ki gayeen? kya ajeeb baat hai ke kalaam ajmi hai aur mukhatib arabi"" inn se kaho yeh quran imaan laane walon ke liye to hadaayat aur Shifa hai, magar jo log imaan nahi laatay unn ke liye yeh kaanon ki dot aur aankhon ki patti hai unn ka haal to aisa hai jaisay unn ko daur se puraka ja raha ho"
41,45,iss se pehlay hum ne moose ko kitaab di thi aur is ke muamlay mein bhi yahi ikhtilaaf howa tha agar tairay rab ne pehlay hi aik baat tey nah kar di hoti to un ikhtilaaf karne walon ke darmain faisla chuka diya jata aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh log uss ki taraf se sakht iztiraab angaiz shak mein parre hue hain
41,46,"jo koi naik amal kere ga apne hi liye acha kere ga, jo badi kere ga is ka wabaal usi par hoga, aur tera rab apne bundon ke haq mein zalim nahi hai"
